B041C016V013	41	16	13	They went and told the rest. But neither did they believe these men.
B041C016V014	41	16	14	Later he appeared to the eleven as they were reclining at table, and reproached them for their lack of faith and dullness of mind because they had not believed those who had seen him since his resurrection.
B041C016V015	41	16	15	He said to them, 
