B044C020V029	44	20	29	I know that after my departure fierce wolves will come among you, not sparing the flock.
B044C020V030	44	20	30	And from among yourselves men will arise speaking perverse things to draw away the disciples after themselves.
B044C020V031	44	20	31	Therefore watch, remembering that for three years I never ceased night nor day to exhort each one of you with tears.
