B066C018V024	66	18	24	In her was found the blood of prophets and of holy men and of all who had been slain on the earth."
B066C019V001	66	19	1	AFTER this I heard what seemed the loud voices of a great multitude in heaven saying, "Hallelujah! Salvation and glory and power belong to our God,
B066C019V002	66	19	2	for true and just are his judgments. He has judged the great prostitute who was corrupting the earth with her lewdness and he has avenged on her the blood of his servants."
